00:09:43,599 --> 00:09:45,119
Yang Xiucheng telah kembali.

93
00:09:46,599 --> 00:09:51,760
Dia menemukan beberapa
petunjuk tentang identitasmu.

94
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:09,320
Ibu Feng.

95
00:10:10,479 --> 00:10:11,280
Nona Feng.

96
